 Social Media Platform

This is a mini full-stack Social Media Platform created as part of the **CodeAlpha Full Stack Development Internship**.

Features

- User can create posts
- View all posts
- Backend API for storing posts
- Frontend and backend integration

Technologies Used

- Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Backend: Node.js, Express.js
- API: REST API

Project Structure

CodeAlpha_SocialMedia/
├── backend/
│   ├── server.js
│   ├── package.json
├── frontend/
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── style.css
│   ├── script.js

How to Run

1. Go to backend directory  
   `cd backend`
2. Install dependencies  
   `npm install`
3. Start server  
   `npm start`
4. Open `frontend/index.html` in browser

